Common.Highlight.Common.Text: +/-175,000 SF of retail space available on Mass Ave, College Ave, 9th Street and Carrollton Ave
Retail suites ranging from 1,000 to 22,000 SF
30,000 SF community-focused food hall and market located in the heart of the development – vendor size ranging from 100–1,000 SF
The modern market will be comprised of two historic garages clad in Art Deco terracotta facades with large roll-up doors allowing for an open-air experience
